{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Rights Beyond Borders: Improve employment policies for international students",
        "additional_details": "- Increase the cap on working hours from 20 to 30 hours per week, allowing students to support themselves financially and gain work experience.\r\n \r\n- Allow international students to engage in independent work and create small businesses.\r\n \r\n- Provide full-time work flexibility by allowing them to work full-time not only during holidays but also during intermission periods.\r\n \r\n- Extend the intermission period from 59 to 120 days to grant students time to manage their studies and prevent burnout.",
        "background": "We want the government to change the employment restriction policies imposed on international students holding a student visa.",
